data.description: *COME ONE, COME ALL:  OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY DEC. 2 from 11am-2pm*  This beautifully remodeled home is priced to sell and just minutes away from downtown and the celebrations of the Holiday cheer at the SA Botanical Gardens Lightscape, The Pearl, Riverwalk, Alamodome, the SA ZOO and so much more!!   Incredible custom upgrades which include contemporary flooring, stainless steel appliances and restored original hardwood floors.  Three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, 1608 sq ft, two living areas, a bonus room/study, and stunning wrap around porch with a large backyard patio.    Items installed in 2019 include the HVAC, the water heater and upgraded electrical, along with a shed in the backyard for extra storage.
